Customize

ggplot(data = mpg, aes(x = displ, y = hwy)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth() + 
  labs(title = "Relationship between engine size and MPG", 
       x = "Highway MPG",
       y = "Engine displacement (litters)") + 
  theme_classic()
